    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资本市场超出预期，加拿大皇家银行超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/rbc-tops-estimates-as-capital-markets-outperform-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行超出了分析师的预期，因为该公司资本市场和财富管理业务的表现强于预期，抵消了贷款损失准备金的增加和费用的增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/rbc-tops-estimates-as-capital-markets-outperform-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Klarna 声称人工智能正在替代客服人员的工作，呼叫中心公司陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/teleperformance-sinks-as-klarna-fuels-worries-over-impact-of-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典金融科技公司 Klarna 发表声明，再次引发人们对人工智能将损害这家法国公司呼叫中心业务的担忧后，Teleperformance SE 股价周三暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/teleperformance-sinks-as-klarna-fuels-worries-over-impact-of-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求宽客逐步取消被认为引发动荡的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/china-tells-quant-funds-to-phase-out-strategy-blamed-for-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国监管机构正在采取措施，逐步缩小流行的量化交易策略的规模，该策略导致了本月中国股市的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/china-tells-quant-funds-to-phase-out-strategy-blamed-for-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:39:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
